'''Aɣyul''' iga yan ɣ imughar li 3ichnin d ufgan arittaws imiddn li zdaghnin ɣ udrar arditawi ikccudn yawid aman ɣ wanu inin ula masd

Aɣyul yan umuder ɣ wanaw n Ayyis, iga amuder ssegman medden, yili yan wanaw yaḍen ittidiren g tagant d isaffen d tnẓruft n tfriqt d asya d imerdal-nnes. aɣyul yamu g wanaw n iyyesan id-emm yan ikfer, yumu g winna issuḍuḍen, ig asmun n umdan aha, ar as ittasey tiɣawsiwin-nnes. ar ttinin i wmeẓẓan n uɣyul asnus.

